examples.en: The toddler scribbled all over the paper.
Someone had scribbled all over my picture.
Someone had scribbled a note in the margin.
He scribbled the number on a scrap of paper.
Paul scribbled his address on the back of an envelope.
Students scribbled furiously as the professor lectured.
He had scribbled his notation so quickly I couldn't read it.
She scribbled a note to him and then dashed off to her meeting.
He scribbled down his phone number.
I scribbled his phone number in my address book.
I scribbled down the telephone number, and now I can't read the figures!
